{
  "stem": "11611.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By June, the United States had taken the position that they had to unconditionally surrender, and the Japanese wanted to guarantee the position of the emperor, which finally we did do.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We maintained the emperor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we wouldn't accept the notion that we would commit ourselves to maintaining the emperor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was the impasse in the negotiations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Japanese knew they were finished as soon as the Germans were finished.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, there wasn't that great of a future in the Japanese war, but they were stubborn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And our people were equally stubborn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We wanted the, the rubric of unconditional surrender, so that was the hang up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some of this, we knew or guessed-- I'm talking about the two of us who were speculating in Hawaii.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were trying to figure out how the hell we were ever going to get home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we did an article for which took a couple months to clear Marine Corps censorship.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Then, we got to and they were ready to publish the article, which was a damn good prescription for how the war actually did end.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the editor of sent it back to us with a couple of suggestions.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We adapted the article to the suggestions, and it passed through censorship again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And by the time it was about finished with censorship, the war ended, which obliterated the article.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's how we occupied our time in between.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when did the war end in the Pacific?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The war ended September 3, 1945.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's my recollection.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hawaii.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What was I doing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I had defended some court martial cases, therefore the Marine Corps punished me by making me a prosecutor of court martial cases.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
